data.description: Gorgeous Sandy home and move in ready. Recently updated (flooring, paint, trim and more)! Bonus sunroom heated with wall heater. Three bedrooms on main level. Fourth bedroom is in the basement with an attached additional living room. Ideal open concept living and kitchen space that is perfect for entertaining. Excellent covered back patio ready for those warm summer nights.  Large backyard for kids and pets. Do not miss this gem! Preferred lender will give $5000 lender credit. TJ Heidenreich 801-694-1733 NMLS 1802412 at Cross Country Mortgage NMLS 3029
